5000|$|<b>Terret</b> blanc {{is a white}} French {{wine grape}} variety growing {{primarily}} in the Languedoc-Roussillon region of southern France. It is a mutation of the <b>Terret</b> vine that also spawned the dark skinned <b>Terret</b> noir and light-skinned <b>Terret</b> gris varieties.|$|E
